{"tid":1847680,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股票、期貨及衍生工具市場明天照常交易","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T07:10:17.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a212d277dca78f49d90e1e0f7cc6aef38f9d83b","tid":1847680,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"香港的股票、期貨及衍生工具市場經過新春假期後，明天（一月二十九日）將如常恢復交易。<br />\n<br />\n因應新型冠狀病毒感染在香港的最新情況，財政司司長今早（一月二十八日）與金融監管機構及香港交易及結算所會面，聽取他們就金融機構預備明天開市的準備和應變工作，以及相關的協調。<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長呼籲各金融機構在可行情況下，作出員工上班特別安排，齊心協力減低疫情在社區擴散的風險。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年1月28日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間13時40分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/28/P2020012800360.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202001%2F28%2FP2020012800360.htm&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtbwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=f6490a4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/28/P2020012800360.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e8658fe70316c98d2c3dd25c8239ed4696131d03","tid":1847680,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"又有得炒股<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d7bc48178de44a8a4dfa1e5815d5ef0f7a4f77","tid":1847680,"uid":187956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"成個政府都係垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}